         This position is responsible for the design, development and testing of databases for software applications focusing on machine data collected from fleets of complex machines. They will work within a software development team and with DBAs, Data Scientists, Software Engineers and Engineering Subject Matter Experts as a database consultant in support of developing new databases or enhancing existing databases.
